Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我果然长胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅 帮我拿下盐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尾巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不哦 盐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天都没怎么吃呀 古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不好好吃饭就会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅你刚刚脱了皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,营养会跟不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,装作不管你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的尾巴更壮实了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅
